[error] /Users/xeno_by/Projects/shapeless-test/Test.scala:13: could not find implicit value for parameter tupleGeneric: shapeless.Generic.Aux[(Int, Char),shapeless.::[Int,shapeless.::[Char,shapeless.HNil]]]
